				</mj-text>

				<mj-image alt="Hyukoh and Sunset Rollercoaster" src="https://github.com/mjcampagna/mjml/blob/main/newsletters/202505/Hyukoh-Sunset-Rollercoaster-hero-credit-Zhong-Lin.jpg?raw=true" />

				<mj-text css-class="article">
					<dl>
						<dt>
							üì∫ 
							<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MUHadUugJ9g">"AAA" by Hyukoh and Sunset Rollercoaster</a>
						</dt>
            <dd>Originally, I was going to feature the song, "Young Man", describing it as, "A feel-good slice of psychedelic dreampop from Korean musician Hyukoh and Taiwanese ensemble Sunset Rollercoaster". Thing is, <cite>AAA</cite> is a spectacular record, front-to-back, brimming with warmth and light, and it deserves to be heard in full. That it comes from the union of representatives from two countries that mean the world to me -- I lived in Korea for over a decade, and my wife is from Taiwan -- makes it all the more special.Sunshine, a soft blanket, a mug of hot chai, and this record. Enjoy!</dd>
					</dl>
